- <a href="https://medium.com/@richardjpope/government-as-a-platform-the-hard-problems-part-3-shared-components-and-apis-9c87dba83e66">Government as a Platform, the hard problems: part 3 – shared components, APIs and the machinery of government</a>
- <a href="https://medium.com/@richardjpope/government-as-a-platform-the-hard-problems-part-4-data-infrastructure-and-registers-8189f9b8ff90">Government as a Platform, the hard problems: part 4 — Data infrastructure and registers</a>
